Detailed Description

cvmx_ase_backdoor_req_data#

The lowest address is first beat (aka control word) and has the SOP. The next address is next beat, etc. The register offset indicated by ASE_BACKDOOR_REQ_CTL[CNT] has the EOP. See further information in ASE_BACKDOOR_REQ_CTL.
